SUMMARY:First Friday Latin Nights at The Velvet Hippo!
DESCRIPTION:Head out to your favorite tropical escape in Downtown Durham for Latin Night every First Friday! Join us as DJ Synko heats up the dance floor\, mixing the best of reggaeton\, bachata\, merengue\, Latin house\, dembow\, cumbia\, and more. Show off your moves\, or just vibe to the music and enjoy creative cocktails and great company. Drink specials\, no cover\, 21+ with valid ID to enter.
