SUMMARY:Grill Out at Ponysaurus Brewing Co.!
DESCRIPTION:We’re firing up the grill and going full New York street cart this Saturday\, March 7 🔥🗽Grilled chicken kabab gyros loaded with marinated chicken\, veggies\, hot sauce\, and that iconic halal white sauce piled high in a warm pita! Grab your plate any time from noon to 3pm!
