SUMMARY:Holi with Viceroy @ Durham Central Park
DESCRIPTION:Get ready to celebrate Holi — the Festival of Colors with Viceroy at Durham Central Park! \nJoin us on Saturday\, March 7th from 2–6pm for an afternoon of color\, music\, food\, and community. This free\, family-friendly event is open to all ages — come dance to a live DJ\, enjoy delicious food and drinks available for purchase\, and take part in the joyful tradition of throwing colors together. \nWe’ll have color powder available for the celebration\, so please do not bring outside colors to the event. Whether you’re celebrating Holi for the first time or continuing a beloved tradition\, everyone is welcome to come experience the fun\, energy\, and togetherness of this vibrant festival! ✨
URL:https://downtowndurham.com/event/holi-with-viceroy-durham-central-park/
