SUMMARY:Craft Club & Supply Swap
DESCRIPTION:Get artsy crafty over a craft beer at our new Craft Club! Bring your own craft to do alongside others – whether it’s knitting\, sewing\, coloring\, painting\, whatever! Show off what you’re working on and learn from the skills of others as you sip cocktails\, brews\, wine\, THC beverages\, and more! \nAnd bonus – every week we’re also hosting a craft swap! Are you a serial hobbyist? Do you have a silly excess of scraps and leftover supplies from discarded crafty projects? How about that pile of things you actually did finish\, but that you can’t possibly use all of? Bring the excess items you’ve made and your spare supplies to trade! Participants will be able to drop their contributions on a reserved table\, and everyone can shop the stash. We will operate on an honor system where everyone is encouraged to take roughly the same value of things they brought. \nEven better\, once a month our Craft Club will also host a workshop on various topics so you can learn and grow as an artist while you have fun. \nSo grab a drink\, get crafty\, and plan to hang out for a while to see who all stops by and what type of goods come through the swap. \n 
URL:https://downtowndurham.com/event/craft-club-supply-swap-2/2026-03-08/
LOCATION:Glass Jug Downtown\, 545 Foster Street\, Suite 10\, Durham\, 27701
CATEGORIES:Art,Craft,Wines, Spirits, Beer and Cheer
