SUMMARY:Recovery: An Afternoon Tea Dance Party!
DESCRIPTION:Mark your calendar for our next day party on Sunday\, March 8th! DJs Gay Agenda and Father Disco bring you Recovery: A Tea Dance from 4pm-8pm. We’ll have drink specials (including mimosa pitchers and spritzes!) all day\, and no cover. Come spill the tea and dance the afternoon away with old friends — and make some new ones along the way! 21+ only with physical ID to enter.
