SUMMARY:Lager & Mexican Dinner at Bull City Burger and Brewery
DESCRIPTION:Bull City Burger and Brewery is hosting a one-night\, white table cloth Lager & Mexican Dinner on Sunday\, March 8 at 5:30pm in downtown Durham. This reservation-only event features a five-course Mexican-inspired dinner paired with four reserve lagers brewed in-house. \nThe evening focuses on the origins and regional influences of Mexican cuisine\, with each course thoughtfully matched to a lager that complements the flavors on the plate. Seating is limited to keep the experience intimate and paced for a full\, guided dinner. \nTickets are $100 per person and include all courses and beer pairings. Advance reservations are required. \nCost: $100 per person\nReservations: Call 919-680-2333\nWebsite: www.bullcityburgerandbrewery.com \nLimited seats available.
